2 │ ALTER TABLE table_name ADD CONSTRAINT field_name_constraint UNIQUE (field_name);
  │                            ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  │
  ╰ help: Create an index `CONCURRENTLY` and create the constraint using the index.
